etz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/israels-central-bank-chief-says-more-clarity-on-defense-spending-needed-amid-gaza-war/0000018e-943a-d229-adae-95fb05260000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军军官在以色列南部发生持刀袭击事件中受轻伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/idf-officer-stabbed-in-suspected-terror-attack-in-southern-israel/0000018e-9372-d4de-afee-f37f57970000</link><description>这名 28 岁的袭击者是贝都因市拉哈特的居民，在刺伤后被枪杀。</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 08:38:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/idf-officer-stabbed-in-suspected-terror-attack-in-southern-israel/0000018e-9372-d4de-afee-f37f57970000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极端正统派领导人表示内塔尼亚胡的联盟不会因正统派军队征兵而崩溃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/as-draft-exemption-expires-ultra-orthodox-leaders-signal-coalition-wont-collapse/0000018e-90dc-d229-adae-91df8bea0000</link><description>尽管以色列极端正统派社区感到愤怒，但联盟领导人并不认为犹太学院学生服兵役的政治危机会对依赖正统政党的总理内塔尼亚胡的联盟构成直接威胁</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 02:43:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/as-draft-exemption-expires-ultra-orthodox-leaders-signal-coalition-wont-collapse/0000018e-90dc-d229-adae-91df8bea0000</guid></item><item><title>为期四天的集会在耶路撒冷拉开帷幕，反内塔尼亚胡抗议运动面临考验</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/anti-netanyahu-govt-protest-to-peak-in-jerusalem-ahead-of-knesset-recess/0000018e-90f5-d9a4-a7bf-dcfdccd30000</link><description>以色列针对内塔尼亚胡政府的抗议运动计划在耶路撒冷议会外建立一个帐篷城，以疏导公众的愤怒，以确保议会春季休会前有强劲的投票率</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 02:43:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article/.premium/anti-netanyahu-govt-protest-to-peak-in-jerusalem-ahead-of-knesset-recess/0000018e-90f5-d9a4-a7bf-dcfdccd30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列辛贝特和摩萨德代表团前往开罗讨论哈马斯人质和停火协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article-live/police-clash-with-anti-govt-protesters-16-arrested-in-tel-aviv/0000018e-9214-d8cd-a9ce-977660560000</link><description>贝尔谢巴疑似刺伤事件造成一人受伤 ■ 以色列代表团预计将前往开罗就停火和释放人质协议进行谈判 ■ 周四西岸枪击事件的嫌疑人自首 ■ 以色列国防军喷气式飞机在叙利亚上空击落可疑空中目标</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 01:30:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-31/ty-article-live/police-clash-with-anti-govt-protesters-16-arrested-in-tel-aviv/0000018e-9214-d8cd-a9ce-977660560000</guid></item><item><title>由于缺乏经济复苏和以色列援助，巴勒斯坦新政府将难以运作</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/lacking-economic-recovery-and-israeli-aid-new-palestinian-govt-will-struggle-to-function/0000018e-90a0-d229-adae-91f35b5b0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦新总理穆罕默德·穆斯塔法称约旦河西岸的经济形势是灾难性的，居民们知道，如果没有国际社会的经济安全网，政府的成功最多也将是有限的</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 20:12:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/lacking-economic-recovery-and-israeli-aid-new-palestinian-govt-will-struggle-to-function/0000018e-90a0-d229-adae-91f35b5b0000</guid></item><item><title>在土地日游行中，数千名巴勒斯坦人和阿拉伯以色列人抗议“种族灭绝”加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/in-land-day-march-thousands-of-palestinians-arab-israelis-protest-gaza-war/0000018e-90c4-d229-adae-91d787070000</link><description>以色列警方允许游行进行，但条件是不得悬挂巴勒斯坦国旗，声称这可能“导致公共秩序混乱”。组织者决定遵守命令，用巴勒斯坦国旗的颜色写反战标语</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 19:55:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/in-land-day-march-thousands-of-palestinians-arab-israelis-protest-gaza-war/0000018e-90c4-d229-adae-91d787070000</guid></item><item><title>数千人在特拉维夫集会，被释放的人质指责内塔尼亚胡政府在加沙抛弃以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/freed-hostage-accuses-govt-of-abandoning-israelis-in-gaza-as-thousands-rally-in-tel-aviv/0000018e-9041-def1-a58f-f47