nvolvement/0000018e-8fb3-def1-a58f-efbb64590000</link><description>联黎部队表示，受伤人员已被疏散接受治疗，目前仍在调查爆炸起因。以色列立即否认参与该事件</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 14:43:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/four-un-staff-wounded-in-unifil-vehicle-strike-in-lebanon-israel-denies-involvement/0000018e-8fb3-def1-a58f-efbb64590000</guid></item><item><title>13岁巴勒斯坦少年在约旦河西岸被枪杀 以色列军队“澄清”事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/13-year-old-palestinian-shot-dead-in-west-bank-israeli-army-clarifying-incident/0000018e-8f9d-d9a4-a7bf-cfdd08110000</link><description>约旦河西岸城镇卡巴蒂亚的消息人士称，以色列军队连夜进行了一次突袭，造成另外两名巴勒斯坦青年受伤，其中一人重伤；另一名巴勒斯坦青年受伤。以色列国防军表示，他们向向他们开枪的恐怖分子进行了还击</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 14:12:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/13-year-old-palestinian-shot-dead-in-west-bank-israeli-army-clarifying-incident/0000018e-8f9d-d9a4-a7bf-cfdd08110000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯人质谈判可能会以新的妥协协议恢复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-set-to-resume-hostage-deal-talks-in-cairo-as-both-sides-seek-compromise/0000018e-8bfc-d9a4-a7bf-cffde55d0000</link><description>一位外国消息人士称，调解员将努力就哈马斯的要求达成妥协，哈马斯的要求使谈判陷入僵局：所有流离失所的巴勒斯坦人返回加沙北部，以色列宣布全面停火</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 06:04:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-hamas-set-to-resume-hostage-deal-talks-in-cairo-as-both-sides-seek-compromise/0000018e-8bfc-d9a4-a7bf-cffde55d0000</guid></item><item><title>服用改变精神药物时经历大规模恐怖袭击是什么感觉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/what-its-like-to-experience-a-mass-terror-attack-while-on-mind-altering-drugs/0000018e-8d49-d782-a7bf-df7f33cf0000</link><description>心理学家兰·萨皮尔正在诺瓦狂欢节治疗 10 月 7 日哈马斯大屠杀的幸存者</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 03:58:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/what-its-like-to-experience-a-mass-terror-attack-while-on-mind-altering-drugs/0000018e-8d49-d782-a7bf-df7f33cf0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战事如火如荼，约旦河西岸却发生了翻天覆地的变化</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-03-30/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/while-war-rages-in-gaza-the-west-bank-has-undergone-a-metamorphosis/0000018e-8d23-d9a4-a7bf-cd7b2c270000</link><description>以色列抓住机会加强占领，大规模逮捕巴勒斯坦人，数百人被杀，并修建了许多新的非法定居者前哨基地和道路。牧羊人被赶出家园，暴力的定居者穿着制服横冲直撞。一切都在战争的庇护下</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 03:04:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-03-30/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/while-war-rages-in-gaza-the-west-bank-has-undergone-a-metamorphosis/0000018e-8d23-d9a4-a7bf-cd7b2c270000</guid></item><item><title>以色列-哈马斯加沙会谈将于周日在开罗恢复；以色列国防军负责人称希法袭击“尚未结束”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article-live/u-s-welcomes-nomination-of-new-palestinian-govt-authorizes-further-munition-to-israel/0000018e-8d17-d229-adae-9dd7e4f10000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，他们在加沙的 Al-Shifa 医院突袭中打死了三名哈马斯高级指挥官。 ■ 黎巴嫩的袭击击中了载有三名联合国观察员和一名翻译的汽车；联黎部队表示正在调查这起爆炸事件，称“不可接受”，因为以色列否认参与此事 ■ 以色列警方逮捕了 16 名涉嫌煽动、支持在圣殿山实施恐怖主义的人 ■ 报告：13 岁巴勒斯坦人在西部被以色列国防军炮火打死银行</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 02:27:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article-live/u-s-welcomes-nomination-of-new-palestinian-govt-authorizes-further-munition-to-israel/0000018e-8d17-d229-adae-9dd7e4f10000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争是极端正统派融入以色列社会的转折点吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/is-the-gaza-war-a-turning-point-in-the-integration-of-haredim-in-israeli-society/0000018e-86a3-db91-afff-afef384d0000</link><description>去年10月，正统派对取消征兵豁免的支持率跃升至创纪录的22%。穿着制服出现在 Bnei Brak 不再是可耻的事情。极端正统社会是否发生了真正的变化？</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 02:13:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-30/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/is-the-gaza-war-a-turning-point-in-the-integration-of-haredim-in-israeli-society/0000018e-86a3-db91-afff-afef384d0000</guid></item><item><title>10名欧洲电视网参赛者在联合声明中呼吁加沙停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/10-eurovision-contestants-call-for-gaza-cease-fire-in-joint-statement/0000018e-8ac3-d9a4-a7bf-cedbb7ad0000</link><description>在回应因以色列参加而退出歌曲比赛的呼声时，这十位艺术家表示，他们想表达“对和平、立即持久停火以及所有人质安全返回的衷心愿望”</description><pubDate>Fri, 29 Mar 2024 17:20:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-29/ty-article/.premium/10-eurovision-contestants-call-for-gaza-cease-fire-in-joint-statement/0000018e-8ac3-d9a4-a7bf-cedbb7ad0000</guid></item></channel></rss>